[SHORT DESC]
Lowers foe's accuracy 1 stage.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Lowers the target's accuracy one stage.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>SmokeScreen has little to no competitive use. Using moves that affect accuracy is an ineffective strategy since many players switch their Pokemon out often, resetting the accuracy boosts.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/sand-attack">Sand-Attack</a> is a Normal-type equivalent.</p>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/flash">Flash</a> is a Normal-type equivalent.</p>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/kinesis">Kinesis</a> is a Normal-type equivalent.</p>